&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Intro 
    &lt;div id=&#34;intro&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before we begin, here&amp;rsquo;s brief intro as to why I care about ricing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In case you didn&amp;rsquo;t know it, I began my &lt;strong&gt;Linux&lt;/strong&gt; journey with &lt;strong&gt;KDE Plasma&lt;/strong&gt; because of the freedom of customization. I love ricing my setups. I hated that &lt;strong&gt;macOS&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;strong&gt;Windows&lt;/strong&gt; did not allow this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And if you want to see what I have managed to do, well, hop on over to my &lt;strong&gt;Layan&lt;/strong&gt; rice&amp;rsquo;s &lt;strong&gt;Githup&lt;/strong&gt; repository, you will get blown away.&lt;/p&gt;
